     const rig = cameraRigRef.current;
     const oc  = orthoCameraRef.current;
     if (rig && oc) {
       const f = rig.orthoFrustum(w / h);
       oc.left = f.left; oc.right = f.right;
       oc.top  = f.top;  oc.bottom = f.bottom;
       oc.updateProjectionMatrix();
     }

5. In the animation tick (where composer.render() is called), sync the
   active camera's position/target from the rig each frame. For ortho mode,
   copy position + lookAt from the perspective camera after the rig updates
